{"tid":1305934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[每日任務] 每日必做, 將抗爭變成生活一部分","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T13:50:27.000Z","uid":18728,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5677873c77d53073c8bfbbbb4ee762629fe00868","tid":1305934,"uid":18728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:39:20.000Z","msg":"除咗主線同支線任務, 每人每日花少少時間做以下嘅事, 成本低, 唔影響正經行動, 只要多人做、長期做, 一定有成效<br />\n<br />\n1. 每日到訪藍絲page, 1 report = 1 support <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 定期去CCTVB廣告客戶FB page表達意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 消費之前, 諗下咩品牌值得支持, 咩品牌有更好代替品 (自從雨革之後, 無幫襯過三中商、Loreal Group, 無睇過CCTVB)<br />\n4. 拒幫襯中國品牌及企業, 包括中資銀行、三中商、海底撈喜茶等等<br />\n5. 有閒錢, 支持下被捕義士、蘋果、立場、Robert Chung、各類有意義眾籌等等<br />\n<br />\n香港人真係好有熱誠, 短期內齊心做一件事好快見成效(例如一日籌到600幾萬登報), 無奈對住共產黨邪惡政權, 係需要有長期抗爭嘅意志, 唔會有一場仗係可以一勞永逸。<br />\n<br />\n只要常存反共嘅心, 無論大環境係點, 每人每日做少少, 就算做唔到加速共產中國衰亡, 至少唔會再助長佢增強。亦想話俾全世界人聽: <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港拒絕融合, Hong Kong is NOT China</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎再加, 集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac68262a736ce88e4f848a3f97567c953c987531","tid":1305934,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c41d313391f5577502354943f46530a6b650a66","tid":1305934,"uid":268855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b47796a670a7abb3bf8c88ac532331e095b174","tid":1305934,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:41:36.0